OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudier than recent days,
OL,6,Fthough sunny spells will develop
OL,7,Fthrough the afternoon. Cloudiest in
OL,8,Fthe north and northwest, with some
OL,9,Flight rain or showers. Warm in central
OL,10,Fand southern Britain.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FLargely cloudy in the north
OL,13,Fwith some patchy drizzle around
OL,14,Fcoasts. Dry elsewhere with clear
OL,15,Fspells. A fresh night for many.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FVariable amounts of cloud in
OL,18,FTuesday with some good sunny spells.
OL,19,FFeel rather warm in the sunshine and
OL,20,Flight winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
